{"id": "art-178", "label": "Art. 178", "title": "Art. 178", "slug": "art-178", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 178 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_278362652\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1984\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_278362652\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorii, respectiv membrii directoratului, sau,\ndup&#259; caz, <span class=SpellE>entit&#259;&#355;ile</span> care <span\nclass=SpellE>&#355;in</span> <span class=SpellE>eviden&#355;a</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionariatului</span> conform prevederilor legale au <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;ia</span> s&#259; pun&#259; la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a\noric&#259;ror <span class=SpellE>al&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>solicitan&#355;i</span>\n<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind structura <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionariatului</span>\nrespectivei <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ns&#259; le elibereze, la cerere, pe cheltuiala lor, certificate privind aceste\ndate.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)De asemenea, sunt <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;i</span> s&#259; pun&#259; la <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> a\n<span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>,\n√Æn <span class=SpellE>acelea&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span>,\nregistrele prev&#259;zute la art. </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>177 alin.\n(1) lit. b) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> f)</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>"}